dc_title_s: Map showing property lines of the Midland Linseed Oil Company
dc_description_s: Tracing of a map showing the property lines, including pier lines, of various company and personal properties, in particular Linseed Oil Company and Valvoline Oil Company.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Compiled by R. Simon May 1919|Plotted by courses and distances shown on survey map by F.A. Dunham June 1911
